<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.8.3">
<l>kaṭikoḷ pūmpoḻil kāmaru poykai vaiku tāmarai vāṅkiya vēḻam</l>
<l>muṭiyum vaṇṇamōr muḻuvali mutalai paṟṟa maṟṟatu niṉcaraṇ niṉaippa</l>
<l>koṭiya vāyvilaṅ kiṉṉuyir malaṅkak koṇṭa cīṟṟamoṉ ṟuṇṭuḷa taṟintuṉ</l>
<l>aṭiya ṉēṉumvan taṭiyiṇai yaṭaintē ṉaṇipo ḻiltiru varaṅkattam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When a huge, powerful crocodile snatched, in a deadly way, an elephant</l>
<l>Which plucked lotuses that grew in a pleasing pool in a garden</l>
<l rend="indent">of fragrance-wafting flowers, as the other meditated on your feet,</l>
<l>There was [such] a rage that seized [you] so that the life</l>
<l rend="indent">of that vicious-mouthed beast perished;</l>
<l>Knowing of that, coming as your servant, I took refuge at your two feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord of sacred Araṅkam with lovely groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
